flowchart TB
    N1["1. Technical objective: Host-side SP1 prover orchestration for creating and checking L2 batch proofs."]
    N2["2. Determinism: same public input and witness produce the same public output and proof"]
    N3["3. Input constraints: L2 batch | guest ELF | prover configuration"]
    N4["4. Transition rule: guest execution is constrained by public values and verifier rules"]
    N5["5. Verifiable output: proof bytes | verification report | state commitment"]
    N6["6. Minimal trust: trust verification keys and verifiers, not prover runtime environments"]
    N7["7. Layer separation: guest proves computation, host orchestrates, L1 verifies compact results"]
    N8["8. Observable evidence: proof id, public output, verification result, duration, and failure reason"]
